## keys() function

Returns an iterator of the own enumerable property names of object.

**Signature:**

```typescript
declare function keys<T extends Record<string, any>>(
  obj: T,
): Generator<Extract<keyof T, string>, void, unknown>;
```

## Example

```ts
[...keys({ a: 1, b: "2", c: true })];
// ["a", "b", "c"]
```
